{panel:title=ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA|titleBGColor=#57d9a3}
*AC1*
*Given* WC1 customer successfully perform a IDV search
*When* Customer lands on the BV / IDV result screen and clicks on export button
*Then* the system should download the PDF and display the user input Information labeled as "Data verified"  and the existing legends i.e  "Match", "Partial Match" , "No Match" & "Unable to Verify" should be part of "Data Verified" section.

*AC1*
*Given* WC1 customer successfully perform a IDV search
*When* Customer lands on the BV result screen and clicks on export button
*Then* the system should download the PDF and display the BDE data labeled as "Matched Business Information"  similar to BV result

NOTE: For PDF report the table can be one below other with any button
